      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable, dependable vehicle that won't break the bank? This car could be just what you need! It's in fair condition \u2014 it runs and drives reliably, though you'll notice some visible wear on both the exterior and interior that reflects its history on the road. Nothing here is hidden: what you see is what you get, and at this price, it offers solid everyday transportation without the premium cost. A great practical choice for a budget-conscious buyer!",
