      "description": "\ud83d\udd27 A Solid Project Car with Potential! \u2014 Looking for a fixer-upper or a parts vehicle? This one could be just what you need! We'll be completely transparent: this car is in poor condition and will require significant repairs to get back on the road. There are visible body damage and wear issues, and the mechanical systems will need attention. That said, it's priced to reflect exactly what it is \u2014 a great opportunity for a skilled DIYer or someone in need of parts. No surprises here, just an honest deal!",
