    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition and is a dependable, practical choice for buyers seeking a reliable used car at a fair price. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 the paint retains a good shine with only minor surface blemishes consistent with normal use, and there are no significant dents or rust concerns. The interior is clean and well-maintained, with seating surfaces showing moderate but normal wear, and all major controls and features functioning as expected. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and reliably, with no warning lights or known mechanical issues. This is a solid everyday driver that has been honestly cared for \u2014 not perfect, but genuinely dependable and ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 31000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly as a car in fair condition, and prospective buyers should read this description carefully before making a purchase decision. The exterior shows noticeable wear, including visible scratches and minor dents that are consistent with years of regular use \u2014 nothing catastrophic, but certainly not pristine. The interior is functional but shows its age, with some wear on the seats, dashboard, and trim pieces. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though buyers should anticipate that some maintenance or repairs may be needed in the near term to keep it reliable. This is a solid option for a buyer looking for basic, functional transportation at an honest price, with realistic expectations about what they're getting.",
      "price": 16000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83c\udf1f Stunning Mint-Condition Gem \u2014 Truly Move-In Ready! \ud83c\udf1f This is the one you've been waiting for \u2014 a genuinely mint-condition vehicle that has been exceptionally well cared for from day one. Every surface, system, and component reflects meticulous maintenance and thoughtful ownership. The paint gleams, the interior is spotless, and everything runs and functions exactly as it should. No surprises, no hidden issues \u2014 just a beautiful, road-ready car that's ready to impress. If you're looking for the best of the best without compromise, this is it. Come see it in person and we're confident you'll agree!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
