    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition and represents a solid, dependable used car for the right buyer. The exterior shows minor wear consistent with normal use \u2014 you may notice a few small scratches or light scuffs here and there, but there are no major dents, rust, or structural damage. The paint retains a reasonable shine and presents well overall. The interior is clean and functional, with moderate wear on high-contact areas like the driver's seat and steering wheel, but no tears, stains, or broken components. Mechanically, the car runs well \u2014 the engine starts reliably, the transmission shifts smoothly, and all major systems are in working order. Some routine maintenance items may be coming due, so a pre-purchase inspection is always encouraged. This is a practical, honest buy for someone looking for a dependable vehicle without the premium price of a mint-condition example.",
